cdata.name: SmartCoin
cdata.desc: SmartCoin (SMC) is a practical digital currency and anonymous peer-to-peer crypto currency designed with a fair start in mind. With it's fast transaction times, ease of use, and good resources SmartCoin is a great everyday use cryptocurrency. The coin was designed to encourage early mining with its super blocks - but ends up being a premine. The block reward is fixed after block 1000 - or roughly a day after its genesis block.
